# Update KAFKA_BROKERS with your MSK or self-managed Kafka endpoint

# Kafka Configuration (Required)
# Example for AWS MSK: kafka-1.xxxxx.kafka.us-east-1.amazonaws.com:9092,kafka-2.xxxxx.kafka.us-east-1.amazonaws.com:9092
